data.description:
PRICE REDUCTION!!!

Seller to offer a 2-1 buydown with seller acceptable offer!!

Welcome to this inviting 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom home that perfectly combines comfort and style. This residence boasts all-new flooring throughout, an enclosed sunroom allowing you to experience the outdoors year-round in the comfort of the enclosed sunroom. Whether you're seeking a tranquil reading space or a vibrant gathering area, this versatile room is perfect for both relaxation and entertainment. This property also includes a convenient storage shed in the backyard. Whether you're a first-time buyer, a growing family, or anyone in between, this property offers the ideal canvas for your lifestyle needs.
